  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd? - \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Plan to remove soldiers from gas stations? - Ministry of Public Security investigates",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Discussions have started regarding the removal of the armed forces who are on duty at the petrol filling stations.",
        "It is understood that the Ministry of Public Security is investigating the matter in response to the request made by various parties including the Sri Lankan Bar Association, focusing on the incidents reported at several fuel filling stations in recent days.",
        "Regarding this, the Secretary of the Ministry of Public Security S. When asked by Hetty Arachi, he said that no final decision has been reached on this matter and that such a decision is likely to be reached in the coming days.",
        "In this situation, it is known that the Ministry of Public Security is investigating to provide special advice to the police to carry out all civil actions through the police and to call the armed forces for help only in case of necessity."
      ],
